import './App.css'
import Cards from './components/Cards.jsx'
import SearchBar from './components/SearchBar.jsx'
import characters from './data.js'
import {Container, ContCartas} from './components/styled-components.jsx'

function App () {
  return (
    <Container className='App' style={{ padding: '25px'}}>
      <ContCartas>
        div 
        <SearchBar
          onSearch={(characterID) => window.alert(characterID)}
        />
    
        <Cards
          characters={characters}
        />
      </ContCartas>
      
      
    </Container>
  )
}

export default App
